{"tid":1290963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣第三波】蔣麗芸全家反共","createTime":"2019-07-06T16:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:03:22.000Z","uid":261349,"like":537,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"b713b776cf78d67242b1e82bb070b57df52d2365","tid":1290963,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:29:32.000Z","msg":"第一，第二波詳情如下，希望文宣組回應：<br />\n【第一波】應中央要求，全面肅整文匯報，大公報，橙新聞，HK G報等勢力！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287959/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287959/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【文宣第二波】鼠王芬都反共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/deRBrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/deRBrS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再講講近來事件</span><br />\n係呢個風頭火勢，蔣麗芸竟然發表恐同言論，矛頭直指岑子杰！<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3444664312226032&amp;id=537711586254667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3444664312226032%26id%3D537711586254667&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=e0bb18ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3444664312226032&amp;id=537711586254667</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">作為保皇黨頭號奴才，點可以就咁放過蔣小姐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，結果一覺唔覺意，比我摷到d咁既野。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蔣小姐既老豆，係老牌既國民黨特務，而且對我地敬愛既中國大陸發動過恐襲行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其後成立「震雄集團」，等自己既子女後代繼承。大家千其唔好相信，呢個係國民黨既殘餘力量蓄意顛覆國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，記住千其唔好整成圖宣揚出去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2014/07/13/78117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2014%2F07%2F13%2F78117&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=50d9a669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2014/07/13/78117</a>"},{"pid":"4bc5a49599515da801357bb35d1991c3ccb5ec42","tid":1290963,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4c2aa187b1f0cc2288b0cf8309fc952d0ffb5b","tid":1290963,"uid":261349,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"大家記住唔好宣揚出去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09d7963132dae058dcb36dc6224342ce0ed431b","tid":1290963,"uid":261349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b197e18495a866ae864ecbe37ba17438316c3e25","tid":1290963,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3027cec1feae1bd4ae957280ec4a7f2ef91ef0ca","tid":1290963,"uid":159913,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"根正苗紅實冇佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢鳩鳩哋藍絲應該都知，矛頭應該指向民建聯"},{"pid":"3ca6ae03b5473262a301f18d374dd8d9fb31ba8a","tid":1290963,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df5c3f83fe59e65e5fc0981eab47f978fa01e0d3","tid":1290963,"uid":10070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":